ygData.messageBody:
Hello everyone I am new to this club and ever
quest. I have a friend who I have been watching play and
now I am dieng to play myself. I just bought the game
and tomorrow will be my first day on. Actually I have
had the game for 4 days but been reading tips and
trying to decide what class to play any suggestions are
appreciated. I was thinking of useing a dwarf enchanter or
dwarf palidin. Hope to see you around and thanks for
the info
